}}'''环球电信'''（Globe Telecom, Inc.）是菲律宾一家[[电信|电信]]服务供应商。该公司是菲律宾最大的[[移动网络|移动网络]]运营商，也是菲律賓最大的固定宽带运营商之一。环球电信通过其[[2G|2G]]、[[3G|3G]]、[[高速封包存取|3.5G]] [[演进式HSPA|HSPA +]]、[[4G|4G]] [[長期演進技術|LTE]]、[[進階長期演進技術|LTE-A]]和[[5G|5G]]网络向用戶提供商用[[無線寬頻|无线寬帶]]服务<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bworldonline.com/globe-telecom-says-5g-service-now-covers-17-cities-nationwide/|title=Globe Telecom says 5G service now covers 17 cities nationwide|work=Business World|date=November 19, 2020|accessdate=2021-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107040609/https://www.bworldonline.com/globe-telecom-says-5g-service-now-covers-17-cities-nationwide/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 截至2020年5月，环球电信的移动用户总数达到8930万<ref>{{Cite web|title=1Q 2020 Analysts' Briefing|url=https://www.globe.com.ph/content/dam/globe/brie/About-us/investor-relations/documents/SEC-PSE-Disclosures/2020/Quarterly/Analysts-Briefing-Materials/GLO-1Q20-Briefing-Materials.pdf|access-date=2021-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108182536/https://www.globe.com.ph/content/dam/globe/brie/About-us/investor-relations/documents/SEC-PSE-Disclosures/2020/Quarterly/Analysts-Briefing-Materials/GLO-1Q20-Briefing-Materials.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

环球电信旗下還有兩個其他業務的部門，其中Globe Studios負責电影和电视制作有關業務，Globe Live負責现场音乐会和音乐活动有關業務<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://entertainment.inquirer.net/196760/globe-reveals-new-content-partners-globe-studios-globe-live|title=Globe reveals new content partners, Globe Studios and Globe Live|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|date=June 29, 2016|accessdate=2021-01-05|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107005714/https://entertainment.inquirer.net/196760/globe-reveals-new-content-partners-globe-studios-globe-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

